name: A.D.D. The Album By AfterDark
description: AfterDark From Southern California is back with a new album titled AfterDark Dominates Dialect. This is a 15 track sound piece reflective of hard hitting beats and non commercial gimmicks. If you are under the impression that a rapper is just a rapper, you are mistaken. AfterDark is what we consider to Be an Emcee. Check out www.myspace.com/afterdark1 or just buy this EPIC album now. You won't take it out of your rotation ever.
